data.text:
Just published - my interview with Robert Chelsea. He is amazing. Robert and I spoke for about 45 minutes. He is a face transplant patient and has a story to tell. https://lnkd.in/gyEQ42-m #podcast #studiocitynow #robertchelsea

Just published ! https://lnkd.in/gqbpQsDr Just published ! Nick Haritatos is amazing. From his move from Greece, Africa and then the United States, he has lived an amazing life. His book, No Limits, talks about his life and businesses. No Limits is the perfect XMAS present, in a gift basket with wine, cheese and bread. Nick also walked the California Trail - a 16 year journey - and we will record another podcast on this. However, No Limits is available on Amazon and where ever you buy your books. Put on your headphones, talk a walk and list to the Nick Haritatos podcast !! #studiocitynow #podcast #nickharitatos #nolimits #amazonbooks
